arts.ttl: Salah scores twice as Egypt qualifies for 2026 World Cup with win over Djibouti
arts.sum: The Liverpool superstar scored twice in a 3-0 victory over Djibouti on Wednesday to ensure Egypt will top its African qualifying group with one round to spare. Egypt will be among nine African teams that directly qualify in the World Cup tournament draw on Dec. 5 in Washington D.C.
